{
  "stem": "15768.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And to this day, I don't know why she was allowed to go to the public school, but it was liberal enough so that she could go.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she became my friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She sat with me on the curb, and helped me learn English, and helped me with my homework.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And when she got through with me, I sounded as though I had just come from Georgia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I had the most fascinating southern accent, and of course, now everybody is again making fun of me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But somehow I didn't-- it didn't matter, and she was a good friend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I went to the principal about four weeks into the struggle and said to him that I wanted to strike a deal with him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "That I would do the work in the grade that I was in, but that he would permit me to give me all the books and all the material pertaining to the next grade, and that I would study that along with my other material.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And when I was ready, I would come to him, and he would give me an exam.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And if I passed that exam, he had to promote me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And must reluctantly, he did, thinking tongue in cheek that this was kind of a strange scheme.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But he-- he entered into it, and this is how I brought myself up to level, is I studied twice as hard and read ahead.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Of course, I lost a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I mean, I couldn't just concentrate on what was being taught.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "American history made absolutely no sense to me because I had no beginning, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But I memorized my material, and I knew-- I thought I knew what I was doing, and so I brought myself up to grade in that manner.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
